sect3.para:
This configuration snippet declares two collection, library_books and library_periodics, both using the
                                BookDocument documen
                            type."collections": [
    {
        "name": "library_books",
        "documentType": "BookDocument"
    },
    {
        "name": "library_periodics",
        "documentType": "BookDocument"
    }
]

To tell an application to use collections:

        {
            "name": "MyLibraryApplication",
            [...]
            "useCollections": {
                "books": "library_books",
                "periodics": "library_periodics"
            }
        }
